      "role": "user",
      "content": "exactly. it's more than just \"symbolic\" though. if u trace the lines from the capitol to the obelisk and then out to the various radial avenues, it forms this very specific geometric shape. it feels like it's meant to focus something. like, if a sigil is designed to channel energy, dc looks like the perfect battery. do u see how the layout creates those specific focal points?",
