      "content": "The layout does create powerful focal points, utilizing axial symmetry to direct visual and conceptual energy towards key monuments. The radial design effectively harnesses the visual momentum generated by the major avenues converging on the central axis. This organization isn't accidental; it's a deliberate architectural statement about power and focus, channeling civic attention through precise lines. The entire city plan functions as a massive, built-in diagram.",
      "source": "target",
