      "content": "a built-in diagram... thats exactly it. but it's not just for \"civic attention.\" if the geometry is designed to channel that kind of energy, what do u think the actual effect is on the people living within it? like, does a layout that intense actually shape the collective consciousness of the people inside the \"battery\"?",
